{"id": 2191, "genre": 1000, "title": "在什么情况下，你会选择性地忽略信息？", "description": "不少网络沟通工具在模拟对话的感觉，但人们最爱的点还是“能够忽略别人发来的消息”。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 15095, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180223155224tpherE043FuPQ6dR.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-02-23T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3769, "title": "在什么情况下，你会选择性地忽略信息？", "content": "在什么情况下，你会选择性地忽略信息？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 266507, "content": "群里@所有人的通知，会等别人搭腔，假装自己不存在", "image": "img/option/option/20180223164609BvmYRJzGDN0QeLVx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266508, "content": "熟人分享的图片、文章，会先忽略想着有空再看", "image": "img/option/option/20180223165352qfCtR3d418nK9gaG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266514, "content": "从点赞到借钱，一切不想答应的要求都装没看到", "image": "img/option/option/20180223165527OhFqL9UTtz2mr1bl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266515, "content": "看起来明显是群发的祝福语或推销信息，大多忽略", "image": "img/option/option/20180223165741v0aqC6SuP3snYbhK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266519, "content": "“在吗”这种没实质内容的问候，会默默等对方接着说", "image": "img/option/option/20180223165816ABEZiRySj5YhC7do.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266521, "content": "工作邮箱收到一时半会解决不了的任务，会先放着", "image": "img/option/option/20180223171507kTOnUmHf6PG8whLr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266524, "content": "陌生未接来电通常都不回，“真有事会再打来的吧”", "image": "img/option/option/20180223170531r1txpAnKULfYqym4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 266526, "content": "短信成验证码和商家促销专用，未读攒几百条也无所谓", "image": "img/option/option/20180223170640T5X2NQjuFI7K6mPC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}